node.text: So excited to try out these @imbuilt Protein and Energy Bars! My favorite flavor so far is the “Mint Brownie Delight.” It tastes so flavorful without being too rich or sweet. I’d recommend starting out with the “10 Bar Sample Box” first in order to decide your flavor preferences for just $14.95. Click the link in my bio and search “10 Bar Sample” and use discount code “AubreyRed” for $5 off your order! Follow @imbuilt for new flavor releases #BuiltBar #ImBuilt #OfficialBuiltBarReview

node.text:
Everything you’ve ever wanted is one step outside your comfort zone. Every single person has their own unique obstacles to overcome and in order to achieve those goals, you have to remain positive and take control of your own life. Negativity will get you nowhere. I love how this video shows different people overcoming their obstacles by choosing happiness. In every situation, we have a choice: negativity or optimism. What would you choose? 
#GaryVee #KSwiss #sponsored #GV004 #positivity #optimism @garyvee @kswiss
